            "title": "Ba Den Mountain",
            "title_i18n": {},
            "details": "Ba Den Mountain, known as the \"Roof of Southern Vietnam\" at 986m, is a premier spiritual and scenic destination in Tay Ninh Province. It features the world's largest cable car station and the tallest bronze Lady Buddha statue in Asia. Visitors come here to enjoy the breathtaking cloud-covered landscapes, explore sacred ancient pagodas, and experience professional trekking trails",
