            "title": "RD Wine Castle",
            "title_i18n": {},
            "details": "The RD Wine Castle (Rang Dong Wine Castle) is a unique luxury attraction located within the Sea Links City complex in Mui Ne. It is the first and only castle of its kind in Vietnam, designed to recreate the atmosphere of a sophisticated California winery.",
            "details_i18n": {},
