        ],
        "notes": "Mui Ne is a captivating coastal paradise that offers a perfect blend of natural wonders and cultural experiences. Visitors can start their journey by walking barefoot through the cool, sandy waters of the Fairy Stream, surrounded by dramatic limestone formations. To catch a glimpse of local life, the Mui Ne Fishing Village provides a vibrant scene of colorful boats and fresh seafood markets. For adventure seekers, the Red Sand Dunes are an ideal spot for sand sliding and witnessing a breathtaking sunset over the vast orange slopes. Finally, a visit to the RD Wine Castle adds a touch of European luxury, where you can explore sophisticated cellars and taste premium wines in a magnificent medieval-style setting",
        "notes_i18n": {}
